SQL_Statement:
SELECT TOP 1_x000D_
 s.instrument, s.bossSpecObjID, px.seeing50, p.psffwhm_r, p.field, p.run, p.camcol, p.rowc_r, p.colc_r, p.rowc, p.colc, p.fracDeV_r, p.deVAB_r, p.deVPhi_r, s.specobjid, s.bestobjid, p.objid, s.plate, s.fiberid, p.insideMask, p.flags, p.sky_r, p.petroFlux_r, p.petroFluxIvar_r, p.fiber2Flux_r, p.petroRad_r, p.petroRadErr_r, p.petroR50_r, p.petroR50Err_r, p.petroR90_r, p.petroR90Err_r, p.deVRad_r, p.deVRadErr_r, p.deVFlux_r, p.deVFluxIvar_r, p.airmass_r, p.cloudCam_r, p.calibStatus_r, s.z, s.zErr, s.zWarning, s.class, s.z_noqso, s.zErr_noqso, s.zWarning_noqso, s.velDisp, s.velDispErr, s.velDispZ, s.velDispZErr, s.velDispChi2, s.velDispNPix, s.velDispDOF, s.snMedian_r, s.snMedian, s.chi68p, s.fracNSigma_1, s.fracNSigHi_1, s.fracNSigLo_1, s.spectroFlux_r, s.spectroSynFlux_r, s.spectroFluxIvar_r, s.spectroSynFluxIvar_r, p.expFlux_r, p.expAB_r, p.expRad_r, p.expPhi_r, p.psfFlux_r_x000D_
FROM PhotoObjAll AS p_x000D_
 JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid JOIN PlateX AS px on px.plateID = s.plateID_x000D_
WHERE _x000D_
 s.scienceprimary = 1_x000D_
 AND s.ra BETWEEN 351.1757441926667 AND 351.17741085933335_x000D_
 AND s.dec BETWEEN 14.607969033866667 AND 14.609635700533332_x000D_
Equivalent_Queries:
SELECT TOP 1
  s.instrument, s.bossSpecObjID, px.seeing50, p.psffwhm_r, p.field, p.run, p.camcol, p.rowc_r, p.colc_r, p.rowc, p.colc, 
  p.fracDeV_r, p.deVAB_r, p.deVPhi_r, s.specobjid, s.bestobjid, p.objid, s.plate, s.fiberid, p.insideMask, p.flags, p.sky_r, 
  p.petroFlux_r, p.petroFluxIvar_r, p.fiber2Flux_r, p.petroRad_r, p.petroRadErr_r, p.petroR50_r, p.petroR50Err_r, p.petroR90_r, 
  p.petroR90Err_r, p.deVRad_r, p.deVRadErr_r, p.deVFlux_r, p.deVFluxIvar_r, p.airmass_r, p.cloudCam_r, p.calibStatus_r, 
  s.z, s.zErr, s.zWarning, s.class, s.z_noqso, s.zErr_noqso, s.zWarning_noqso, s.velDisp, s.velDispErr, s.velDispZ, s.velDispZErr, 
  s.velDispChi2, s.velDispNPix, s.velDispDOF, s.snMedian_r, s.snMedian, s.chi68p, s.fracNSigma_1, s.fracNSigHi_1, s.fracNSigLo_1, 
  s.spectroFlux_r, s.spectroSynFlux_r, s.spectroFluxIvar_r, s.spectroSynFluxIvar_r, p.expFlux_r, p.expAB_r, p.expRad_r, 
  p.expPhi_r, p.psfFlux_r
FROM 
  PhotoObjAll AS p, SpecObjAll AS s, PlateX AS px
WHERE 
  s.bestobjid = p.objid AND

  s.scienceprimary = 1 AND 
  s.ra BETWEEN 351.1757441926667 AND 351.17741085933335 AND

SQL_Statement: select star.objID, star.rowc, star.colc, star.ra, star.dec, star.u, star.g, star.r, star.i, star.z, SpecObj.class, SpecObj.fiberID, SpecObj.mjd, SpecObj.run2d, SpecObj.plate, star.b, star.nObserve, star.nDetect, star.nEdge, star.score, star.nChild, star.probPSF from star, SpecObj where star.objID = specObj.targetObjID and SpecObj.fiberID = 596 and SpecObj.mjd = 55359 and SpecObj.run2d = 'v5_10_0' and SpecObj.plate = 4055
Equivalent_Queries:
WITH cte AS (
    SELECT 
        star.objID, 
        star.rowc, 
        star.colc, 
        star.ra, 
        star.dec, 
        star.u, 
        star.g, 
        star.r, 
        star.i, 
        star.z, 
        SpecObj.class, 
        SpecObj.fiberID, 
        SpecObj.mjd, 
        SpecObj.run2d, 
        SpecObj.plate, 
        star.b, 
        star.nObserve, 
        star.nDetect, 
        star.nEdge, 
        star.score, 
        star.nChild, 
        star.probPSF 
    FROM 
        star
    JOIN 
        SpecObj 
    ON 
        star.objID = SpecObj.targetObjID 
    WHERE 
        SpecObj.fiberID = 596 
        AND SpecObj.mjd = 55359 
        AND SpecObj.run2d = 'v5_10_0' 
        AND SpecObj.plate = 4055
)
SELECT * FROM cte;

SQL_Statement: SELECT TOP 10000 s.plate, s.fiberid, s.mjd, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.zwarning, g.h_beta_flux, g.h_alpha_flux, g.h_beta_flux_err, g.h_alpha_flux_err, e.bptclass, e.lgm_tot_p50, i.lick_hd_a_sub, i.d4000_n_sub, i.lick_hd_a_sub_err, i.d4000_n_sub_err, p.petror90_r FROM GalSpecLine AS g, SpecObj AS s, GalSpecExtra AS e, GalSpecIndx AS i, galaxy AS p WHERE s.specobjid = g.specobjid AND s.specobjid = e.specobjid AND s.specobjid = i.specobjid AND s.bestobjid = p.objid AND bptclass = 1 AND s.z BETWEEN 0.04 and 0.1 AND h_alpha_flux > h_alpha_flux_err*5.0 AND h_beta_flux > h_beta_flux_err*5.0 AND d4000_n_sub > d4000_n_sub_err*5.0 AND h_alpha_flux_err > 0 AND h_beta_flux_err > 0 AND h_alpha_flux > 2.7*h_beta_flux AND lgm_tot_p50 > 0 AND sigma_balmer < 509.55 AND s.class = 'GALAXY' AND s.zwarning = 0
Equivalent_Queries:
SELECT TOP 10000 
    s.plate, 
    s.fiberid, 
    s.mjd, 
    s.ra, 
    s.dec, 
    s.z, 
    s.zwarning, 
    g.h_beta_flux, 
    g.h_alpha_flux, 
    g.h_beta_flux_err, 
    g.h_alpha_flux_err, 
    e.bptclass, 
    e.lgm_tot_p50, 
    i.lick_hd_a_sub, 
    i.d4000_n_sub, 
    i.lick_hd_a_sub_err, 
    i.d4000_n_sub_err, 
    p.petror90_r
FROM 
    SpecObj AS s
JOIN 
    (SELECT specobjid, h_beta_flux, h_alpha_flux, h_beta_flux_err, h_alpha_flux_err 
     FROM GalSpecLine 
     WHERE h_alpha_flux > h_alpha_flux_err * 5.0 
       AND h_beta_flux > h_beta_flux_err * 5.0 
       AND h_alpha_flux > 2.7 * h_beta_flux 
       AND h_alpha_flux_err > 0 
       AND h_beta_flux_err > 0) AS g 
    ON s.specobjid = g.specobjid
JOIN 
    (SELECT specobjid, bptclass, lgm_tot_p50 
     FROM GalSpecExtra 
     WHERE bptclass = 1 
       AND lgm_tot_p50 > 0) AS e 
    ON s.specobjid = e.specobjid
JOIN 
    (SELECT specobjid, lick_hd_a_sub, d4000_n_sub, lick_hd_a_sub_err, d4000_n_sub_err 
     FROM GalSpecIndx 
     WHERE d4000_n_sub > d4000_n_sub_err * 5.0) AS i 
    ON s.specobjid = i.specobjid
JOIN 
    (SELECT objid, petror90_r 
     FROM galaxy) AS p 
    ON s.bestobjid = p.objid
WHERE 
    s.z BETWEEN 0.04 AND 0.1 
    AND s.class = 'GALAXY' 
    AND s.zwarning = 0 
    AND sigma_balmer < 509.55;

SQL_Statement: select top 12000 p.objid, p.field, p.ra, p.dec, p.b, p.l, p.run, p.mjd, s.plate, s.fiberid, s.z, s.class from specobj as s join photoobj as p on p.objid=s.bestobjid where p.ra between 150 and 240 and p.dec between 0 and 3 and s.z between 0.005 and 0.2 and p.r between 13.5 and 17.7
Equivalent_Queries:
SELECT TOP 12000 
    p.objid, 
    p.field, 
    p.ra, 
    p.dec, 
    p.b, 
    p.l, 
    p.run, 
    p.mjd, 
    s.plate, 
    s.fiberid, 
    s.z, 
    s.class 
FROM 
    photoobj AS p
JOIN 
    (SELECT specobjid, bestobjid, plate, fiberid, z, class 
     FROM specobj 
     WHERE z BETWEEN 0.005 AND 0.2) AS s 
    ON p.objid = s.bestobjid
WHERE 
    p.ra BETWEEN 150 AND 240 
    AND p.dec BETWEEN 0 AND 3 
    AND p.r BETWEEN 13.5 AND 17.7;

SQL_Statement: SELECT top 20 specObjID, fiberID, mjd, plate, run2d, ra, dec FROM SpecObj WHERE run2d='v5_13_2' AND ra BETWEEN 200 AND 220
Equivalent_Queries:
SELECT TOP 20 specObjID, fiberID, mjd, plate, run2d, ra, dec
FROM (
    SELECT specObjID, fiberID, mjd, plate, run2d, ra, dec
    FROM SpecObj
    WHERE run2d = 'v5_13_2'
    INTERSECT
    SELECT specObjID, fiberID, mjd, plate, run2d, ra, dec
    FROM SpecObj
    WHERE ra BETWEEN 200 AND 220 AND run2d = 'v5_13_2'  -- Ensuring both conditions are matched in both subqueries
) AS intersected_results
ORDER BY specObjID;  -- A specific order to mimic the default behavior of the first query if needed

SQL_Statement: select top 12000 objid, z,((z+1)*(z+1)-1)/((z+1)*(z+1)+1) as z_zr, ((z+1)*(z+1)-1)/((z+1)*(z+1)+1)*299792 as Kmsec_zr, ((z+1)*(z+1)-1)/((z+1)*(z+1)+1)*299792/67.4 as DistMpc_zr, ((z+1)*(z+1)-1)/((z+1)*(z+1)+1)*299792*3.26/67.4 as DistMly_zr, ra, dec, class,subclass, psfmag_r from specphoto where ra between 150 and 240 and dec between 0 and 3 and z between 0.005 and 0.2 and psfmag_r between 13.5 and 17.7
Equivalent_Queries:
SELECT TOP 12000 
    objid, 
    z,
    CASE 
        WHEN z IS NOT NULL THEN ((z+1)*(z+1)-1)/((z+1)*(z+1)+1)
        ELSE NULL 
    END as z_zr,
    CASE 
        WHEN z IS NOT NULL THEN ((z+1)*(z+1)-1)/((z+1)*(z+1)+1) * 299792
        ELSE NULL 
    END as Kmsec_zr,
    CASE 
        WHEN z IS NOT NULL THEN ((z+1)*(z+1)-1)/((z+1)*(z+1)+1) * 299792 / 67.4
        ELSE NULL 
    END as DistMpc_zr,
    CASE 
        WHEN z IS NOT NULL THEN ((z+1)*(z+1)-1)/((z+1)*(z+1)+1) * 299792 * 3.26 / 67.4
        ELSE NULL 
    END as DistMly_zr,
    ra, 
    dec, 
    class,
    subclass, 
    psfmag_r 
FROM 
    specphoto 
WHERE 
    ra BETWEEN 150 AND 240 
    AND dec BETWEEN 0 AND 3 
    AND z BETWEEN 0.005 AND 0.2 
    AND psfmag_r BETWEEN 13.5 AND 17.7;

SQL_Statement: select name from sysobjects where type='p' and category=0 order by name asc
Equivalent_Queries:
SELECT 
    CASE 
        WHEN type = 'p' AND category = 0 THEN name
        ELSE name -- This will never be executed due to the WHERE clause
    END AS name
FROM 
    sysobjects 
WHERE 
    type = 'p' 
    AND category = 0 
ORDER BY 
    name ASC;

FROM DBObjects dbo1

)

SQL_Statement:
SELECT u.up_name as name, _x000D_
 p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,_x000D_
 dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type,_x000D_
 p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z_x000D_
FROM #upload u_x000D_
 JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id_x000D_
 JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID_x000D_
ORDER by x.up_id_x000D_
','5000', @log=0, @filter=1
Equivalent_Queries:
WITH CombinedData AS (
    SELECT 
        u.up_name as name,
        p.objID, 
        p.ra, 
        p.dec, 
        p.run, 
        p.rerun, 
        p.camcol, 
        p.field,
        dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type,
        p.modelMag_u, 
        p.modelMag_g, 
        p.modelMag_r, 
        p.modelMag_i, 
        p.modelMag_z
    FROM 
        #upload u
        JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id
        JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID
)
SELECT * 
FROM CombinedData
ORDER BY up_id;

SQL_Statement: SELECT DISTINCT s.run2d, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberID FROM PhotoObjAll AS p JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID WHERE (s.plate=421 AND s.mjd=51821 AND s.fiberid=180)
Equivalent_Queries:
SELECT DISTINCT 
    s.run2d, 
    s.plate, 
    s.mjd, 
    CASE 
        WHEN s.fiberID IS NOT NULL THEN s.fiberID
        ELSE 0 -- This case will not occur as fiberID seems to be always present, but it illustrates the use of CASE
    END AS fiberID
FROM PhotoObjAll AS p 
JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID
WHERE (s.plate=421 AND s.mjd=51821 AND s.fiberid=180)

SQL_Statement: SELECT DISTINCT p.ra, p.dec, p.objid, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, s.z, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberID, s.specobjid, s.run2d FROM PhotoObjAll AS p JOIN SpecObjAll s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID WHERE (s.plate=7405 AND s.mjd=57134 AND s.fiberid=759)
Equivalent_Queries:
SELECT DISTINCT 
    p.ra, p.dec, p.objid, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, 
    s.z, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberID, s.specobjid, s.run2d
FROM 
    PhotoObjAll AS p
JOIN
    SpecObjAll AS s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID
WHERE 
    EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM SpecObjAll AS s2
        WHERE 
            s2.bestObjID = p.objID
            AND s2.plate = 7405 
            AND s2.mjd = 57134 
            AND s2.fiberid = 759
    )
    AND s.plate = 7405 
    AND s.mjd = 57134 
    AND s.fiberid = 759

SELECT u.up_name as name, _x000D_
 p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,_x000D_
 dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type,_x000D_
 p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z_x000D_
FROM #upload u_x000D_
 JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id_x000D_
 JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID_x000D_
ORDER by x.up_id_x000D_
','500000', @log=0, @filter=1
Equivalent_Queries:
WITH CombinedData AS (
    SELECT 
        u.up_name as name,
        p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,
        dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type,
        p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z,
        x.up_id
    FROM #upload u
    JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id
    JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID
)
SELECT 
    name, objID, ra, dec, run, rerun, camcol, field, type,
    modelMag_u, modelMag_g, modelMag_r, modelMag_i, modelMag_z
FROM CombinedData
ORDER BY up_id;

  dbo.fGetUrlFitsCFrame(f.fieldId,'u') as u_url,

	dbo.fGetUrlFitsCFrame(f.fieldId,'r') as r_url,
	dbo.fGetUrlFitsCFrame(f.fieldId,'i') as i_url,

        s.plate, 
        s.mjd,

SQL_Statement:
SELECT TOP 10000
  p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,
  p.Err_u, p.Err_g, p.Err_r,p.Err_i,p.Err_z
  p.obj,cast(str(p.ra,13,8) as float) as ra,cast(str(p.[dec],13,8) as float) as dec,p.r,
  ISNULL(s.z,0) as redshift,ISNULL(s.zErr,0) as redshiftErr,ISNULL(s.zWarning,0) as zWarning,
  ISNULL(s.class,0) as class, p.score as score, c.z, c.zErr from PhotoObj AS p 
  LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecObj s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID 
  JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(10.458750,-9.301944,60.0) AS b ON  b.objID = P.objID 
  JOIN Photoz as c ON c.objID = P.objID
  WHERE  p.u < 24 AND p.g < 24 AND p.r < 24 AND p.i < 24 AND p.z < 24 AND (p.type = 3)
Equivalent_Queries:
WITH NearbyObjects AS (
    SELECT
        p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z,
        p.Err_u, p.Err_g, p.Err_r, p.Err_i, p.Err_z,
        p.obj, CAST(STR(p.ra, 13, 8) AS FLOAT) AS ra, CAST(STR(p.dec, 13, 8) AS FLOAT) AS dec, p.r,
        ISNULL(s.z, 0) AS redshift, ISNULL(s.zErr, 0) AS redshiftErr, ISNULL(s.zWarning, 0) AS zWarning,
        ISNULL(s.class, 0) AS class, p.score AS score, c.z, c.zErr
    FROM PhotoObj AS p
    LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecObj AS s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID
    JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(10.458750, -9.301944, 60.0) AS b ON b.objID = p.objID
    JOIN Photoz AS c ON c.objID = p.objID
    WHERE p.u < 24 AND p.g < 24 AND p.r < 24 AND p.i < 24 AND p.z < 24 AND (p.type = 3)
)
SELECT TOP 10000
    u, g, r, i, z,
    Err_u, Err_g, Err_r, Err_i, Err_z,
    obj, ra, dec, r,
    redshift, redshiftErr, zWarning,
    class, score, z, zErr
FROM NearbyObjects;

SQL_Statement: select top 1 objid, z, zerr, photoerrorclass from photoz where objid=1237654391103553664
Equivalent_Queries:
WITH SelectedPhotoZ AS (
    SELECT objid, z, zerr, photoerrorclass
    FROM photoz
    WHERE objid = 1237654391103553664
)
SELECT TOP 1 objid, z, zerr, photoerrorclass
FROM SelectedPhotoZ;

SQL_Statement: SELECT DISTINCT s.run2d, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberID FROM PhotoObjAll AS p JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID WHERE (s.plate=657 AND s.mjd=52177 AND s.fiberid=411)
Equivalent_Queries:
SELECT DISTINCT s.run2d, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberID 
FROM SpecObjAll AS s 
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1 
    FROM PhotoObjAll AS p 
    WHERE p.objID = s.bestObjID
) AND s.plate = 657 AND s.mjd = 52177 AND s.fiberid = 411;

SQL_Statement: select top 1 objid, z, zerr, photoerrorclass from photoz where objid=1237662237467345440
Equivalent_Queries:
SELECT TOP 1 objid, z, zerr, photoerrorclass 
FROM photoz p
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM photoz 
    WHERE objid = p.objid AND objid = 1237662237467345440
)

SQL_Statement: select top 1 p.objid, s.z, s.zerr, s.class, s.zwarning from photoobj as p join specobj as s on s.bestobjid = p.objid where p.objid=1237655109451383111
Equivalent_Queries:
SELECT TOP 1
    p.objid,
    sub.z,
    sub.zerr,
    sub.class,
    sub.zwarning
FROM photoobj AS p
CROSS APPLY (
    SELECT TOP 1 s.z, s.zerr, s.class, s.zwarning
    FROM specobj s
    WHERE s.bestobjid = p.objid
) AS sub
WHERE p.objid = 1237655109451383111;

SQL_Statement: SELECT DISTINCT p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field FROM PhotoObjAll AS p WHERE (p.run=3716 AND p.camcol=6 AND p.field=213 AND p.rerun=301)
Equivalent_Queries:
SELECT DISTINCT 
    p.run, 
    p.rerun, 
    p.camcol, 
    p.field 
FROM PhotoObjAll AS p 
WHERE 1 = CASE 
    WHEN p.run=3716 AND p.camcol=6 AND p.field=213 AND p.rerun=301 THEN 1
    ELSE 0
END;

SQL_Statement:
SELECT TOP 20000 p.objid,
 p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, p.obj,
 p.type, p.ra, p.dec, p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,
 p.Err_u, p.Err_g, p.Err_r,p.Err_i,p.Err_z
 FROM fGetNearbyObjEq(81.2100326628349,-45.9966228663745,12.7221609390468) n, PhotoPrimary p
 WHERE n.objID=p.objID AND p.u between 0 AND 22
Equivalent_Queries:
WITH NearbyObjects AS (
    SELECT 
        p.objid,
        p.run, 
        p.rerun, 
        p.camcol, 
        p.field, 
        p.obj,
        p.type, 
        p.ra, 
        p.dec, 
        p.u, 
        p.g, 
        p.r, 
        p.i, 
        p.z,
        p.Err_u, 
        p.Err_g, 
        p.Err_r, 
        p.Err_i, 
        p.Err_z
    FROM 
        fGetNearbyObjEq(81.2100326628349, -45.9966228663745, 12.7221609390468) n
    JOIN 
        PhotoPrimary p ON n.objID = p.objID
    WHERE 
        p.u BETWEEN 0 AND 22
)

SELECT TOP 20000
    objid,
    run, 
    rerun, 
    camcol, 
    field, 
    obj,
    type, 
    ra, 
    dec, 
    u, 
    g, 
    r, 
    i, 
    z,
    Err_u, 
    Err_g, 
    Err_r, 
    Err_i, 
    Err_z
FROM 
    NearbyObjects;

SQL_Statement: SELECT DISTINCT p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field FROM PhotoObjAll AS p WHERE (p.run=2126 AND p.camcol=1 AND p.field=441 AND p.rerun=301)
Equivalent_Queries:
SELECT DISTINCT p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field 
FROM PhotoObjAll AS p 
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1 
    FROM PhotoObjAll AS sub
    WHERE sub.run = p.run 
      AND sub.rerun = p.rerun 
      AND sub.camcol = p.camcol 
      AND sub.field = p.field 
      AND sub.run = 2126 
      AND sub.camcol = 1 
      AND sub.field = 441 
      AND sub.rerun = 301
);

SQL_Statement: SELECT TOP 500 ra,dec,u,err_u,g,err_g,r,err_r,i,err_i,z,err_z FROM PhotoObJ WHERE ra BETWEEN 227.12910 AND 227.41500 AND dec BETWEEN 52.45760 AND 52.63079 AND z>15.2 AND z<19.2 AND err_z<0.1 AND clean=1 ORDER BY z
Equivalent_Queries:
WITH FilteredPhotoObj AS (
    SELECT 
        ra, 
        dec, 
        u, 
        err_u, 
        g, 
        err_g, 
        r, 
        err_r, 
        i, 
        err_i, 
        z, 
        err_z
    FROM 
        PhotoObj
    WHERE 
        ra BETWEEN 227.12910 AND 227.41500 
        AND dec BETWEEN 52.45760 AND 52.63079 
        AND z > 15.2 
        AND z < 19.2 
        AND err_z < 0.1 
        AND clean = 1
)

SELECT TOP 500
    ra,
    dec,
    u,
    err_u,
    g,
    err_g,
    r,
    err_r,
    i,
    err_i,
    z,
    err_z
FROM 
    FilteredPhotoObj
ORDER BY 
    z;

SQL_Statement: SELECT DISTINCT s.run2d, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberID FROM PhotoObjAll AS p JOIN SpecObjAll s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID WHERE (s.plate=9430 AND s.mjd=58112 AND s.fiberid=143)

SQL_Statement:
SELECT p.*
FROM PhotoObj AS p
WHERE p.objID IN (
    SELECT s.objID
    FROM SpecObj AS s
    WHERE s.objType = 6 -- Stars
    AND s.objID IN (
        SELECT f.objID
        FROM Field AS f
        WHERE f.ra BETWEEN 150 AND 160
        AND f.fieldID IN (
            SELECT fieldID
            FROM Galaxy
            WHERE petromag_r < 15
        )
    )
);
Equivalent_Queries:
SELECT p.*
FROM PhotoObj AS p
JOIN SpecObj AS s ON p.objID = s.objID
JOIN Field AS f ON s.objID = f.objID
JOIN Galaxy AS g ON f.fieldID = g.fieldID
WHERE s.objType = 6 -- Stars
AND f.ra BETWEEN 150 AND 160
AND g.petromag_r < 10;

SQL_Statement:
SELECT q.*
FROM SpecObj AS q
WHERE q.class = 'QSO'
AND q.z > 2.0
AND q.objID IN (
    SELECT p.objID
    FROM PhotoObj AS p
    WHERE p.petromag_g < 20
    AND p.objID IN (
        SELECT f.objID
        FROM Field AS f
        WHERE f.ra BETWEEN 100 AND 200
        AND f.dec BETWEEN -10 AND 10
    )
);
Equivalent_Queries:
SELECT q.*
FROM SpecObj AS q
WHERE q.class = 'QSO'
AND q.z > 2.0
AND q.objID IN (
    SELECT p.objID
    FROM PhotoObj AS p
    WHERE p.petromag_g > 20
    AND p.objID IN (
        SELECT f.objID
        FROM Field AS f
        WHERE f.ra BETWEEN 100 AND 200
        AND f.dec BETWEEN -10 AND 10
    )
);

SQL_Statement:
SELECT g.*
FROM Galaxy AS g
WHERE g.petromag_r BETWEEN 14 AND 18
AND g.objID IN (
    SELECT s.objID
    FROM SpecObj AS s
    WHERE s.class = 'GALAXY'
    AND s.objID IN (
        SELECT p.objID
        FROM PhotoObj AS p
        WHERE p.mode = 1 -- Primary objects
        AND p.objID IN (
            SELECT f.objID
            FROM Field AS f
            WHERE f.ra BETWEEN 120 AND 180
            AND f.dec BETWEEN 0 AND 50
        )
    )
);
Equivalent_Queries:
SELECT g.*
FROM Galaxy AS g
WHERE g.petromag_r BETWEEN 14 AND 18
AND g.objID IN (
    SELECT s.objID
    FROM SpecObj AS s
    WHERE s.class = 'GALAXY'
    AND s.objID IN (
        SELECT p.objID
        FROM PhotoObj AS p
        WHERE p.mode = 2 -- Primary objects
        AND p.objID IN (
            SELECT f.objID
            FROM Field AS f
            WHERE f.ra BETWEEN 120 AND 180
            AND f.dec BETWEEN 0 AND 50
        )
    )
);

SQL_Statement:
SELECT p.*
FROM PhotoObj AS p
WHERE p.objID IN (
    SELECT s1.objID
    FROM SpecObj AS s1
    WHERE s1.z > 0.5
    AND s1.objID IN (
        SELECT s2.objID
        FROM SpecObj AS s2
        WHERE s2.petromag_r < 19
        AND s2.objID IN (
            SELECT g.objID
            FROM Galaxy AS g
            WHERE g.ra BETWEEN 180 AND 240
            AND g.dec BETWEEN -20 AND 20
            AND g.objID IN (
                SELECT f.objID
                FROM Field AS f
                WHERE f.fieldID IN (
                    SELECT fieldID
                    FROM Field
                    GROUP BY fieldID
                    HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
                )
            )
        )
    )
);
Equivalent_Queries:
WITH FieldCTE AS (
    SELECT f.objID
    FROM Field AS f
    WHERE f.fieldID IN (
        SELECT fieldID
        FROM Field
        GROUP BY fieldID
        HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
    )
),
GalaxyCTE AS (
    SELECT g.objID
    FROM Galaxy AS g
    JOIN FieldCTE AS f ON g.objID = f.objID
    WHERE g.ra BETWEEN 180 AND 240
    AND g.dec BETWEEN -20 AND 20
),
SpecObjCTE AS (
    SELECT s.objID
    FROM SpecObj AS s
    JOIN GalaxyCTE AS g ON s.objID = g.objID
    WHERE s.z > 0.5
    AND s.objID IN (
        SELECT s2.objID
        FROM SpecObj AS s2
        WHERE s2.petromag_r < 19
    )
)
SELECT p.*
FROM PhotoObj AS p
JOIN SpecObjCTE AS s ON p.objID = s.objID;

SQL_Statement:
SELECT p.*
FROM PhotoObj AS p
WHERE p.objID IN (
    SELECT s.objID
    FROM SpecObj AS s
    WHERE s.class = 'STAR'
    AND s.zWarning = 0
    AND s.objID IN (
        SELECT g.objID

);

FROM SpecObj AS s1
WHERE s1.class = 'STAR'
AND s1.objID IN (
    SELECT s2.objID
    FROM SpecObj AS s2
    WHERE s2.zWarning = 0
    AND s2.objID IN (
        SELECT g.objID
        FROM Galaxy AS g
        WHERE g.petromag_r < 19
        AND g.objID IN (
            SELECT p.objID
            FROM PhotoObj AS p
            WHERE p.mode = 1
            AND p.objID IN (
                SELECT f.objID
                FROM Field AS f
                WHERE f.ra BETWEEN 120 AND 160
                AND f.dec BETWEEN -10 AND 10
                AND f.fieldID IN (
                    SELECT fieldID
                    FROM PhotoObj
                    WHERE run = 700
                )
            )
        )
    )
);

FROM SpecObj AS s1
JOIN SpecObj AS s2 ON s1.objID = s2.objID
JOIN Galaxy AS g ON s2.objID = g.objID
JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON g.objID = p.objID
JOIN Field AS f ON p.objID = f.objID
JOIN PhotoObj AS p2 ON f.fieldID = p2.fieldID
WHERE s1.class = 'STAR'
AND s2.zWarning = 0
AND g.petromag_r < 19
AND p.mode = 1
AND f.ra BETWEEN 120 AND 160
AND f.dec BETWEEN -10 AND 10
AND p2.run = 700;
